The third and final stage, HA, consists of a fusion-in-decoder (FiD) model [izacard2021leveraging], that is state-of-the-art in the retrieve-and-read paradigm for open-domain QA.
FiD acts as a ``generative reader'', creating a crisp answer from the top-{{2204.11677_FO0022||FO}} evidences, that is returned to the end user.